{"tid":41943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三地警方破網上情緣騙案七十三宗在港發生","createTime":"2016-12-16T09:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T19:20:49.000Z","uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3df9491af13b196ad6f65fcbd197477b826654","tid":41943,"uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"本港警方上月底聯同馬來西亞及尼日利亞警方，合力打撃網上情緣騙案，在馬來西亞及尼日利亞共拘捕十四人，涉及騙案達八十六宗，涉款六千多萬港元；<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">當中七十三宗在香港發生</span></span>，共涉及五千八百萬元，其中一宗涉款達九百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，受害人多數都是女性，學歷較高，並用英文與騙徒溝通。騙徒訛稱是來自歐美的專業人士，在東南亞工作，以郵包被扣要交關稅及金錢援助等藉口，要求事主匯款，其後不知所終。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港女真係特別on9<br />\n只要唔係香港人 連黑鬼阿差都食"},{"pid":"e43b005f14eba51248243afbe3295f6a02a57341","tid":41943,"uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d767542de31abaf65f6ac0c7a899fa37ef115a0","tid":41943,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0280ec27ea6349ea8bbc6032689b8a1ccc24bf2f","tid":41943,"uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>涉款六千多萬港元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畀我好過啦屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"996c8de4d23c18741121b73c62e16ab9cbacf053","tid":41943,"uid":2167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"港女on9呢d野你識條...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa5fb29ca44131f1f50c621cdef6b3ed245236a","tid":41943,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:01:57.000Z","msg":"港女寧願俾鬼佬呃都唔肯同港男一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1dd165fb05e29debd5dbc7fd7a2a3b82d70a9f","tid":41943,"uid":17947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T13:49:59.000